--
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `vistaacta`;

CREATE ALGORITHM=UNDEFINED DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` SQL SECURITY DEFINER VIEW `vistaacta`  AS  select `actas`.`id_act` AS `id_act`,`actas`.`can_act` AS `can_act`,`actas`.`rec_act` AS `rec_act`,`actas`.`jun_act` AS `jun_act`,`detalleactas`.`ced_per` AS `ced_per`,`detalleactas`.`vot_act` AS `vot_act`,`datospersonales`.`nom_per` AS `nom_per` from ((`actas` join `detalleactas`) join `datospersonales`) where ((`detalleactas`.`id_act` = `actas`.`id_act`) and (`detalleactas`.`ced_per` = `datospersonales`.`ced_per`)) ;

--
-- Estructura para la vista `vistacandidatos`
--
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `vistacandidatos`;

CREATE ALGORITHM=UNDEFINED DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` SQL SECURITY DEFINER VIEW `vistacandidatos`  AS  select `candidatos`.`id_can` AS `id_can`,`datospersonales`.`ced_per` AS `ced_per`,`datospersonales`.`nom_per` AS `nom_per`,`datospersonales`.`mail_per` AS `mail_per`,`datospersonales`.`tel_per` AS `tel_per`,`datospersonales`.`edad_per` AS `edad_per`,`candidatos`.`dig_can` AS `dig_can`,`candidatos`.`pri_sec` AS `pri_sec`,`candidatos`.`lis_can` AS `lis_can`,`candidatos`.`nom_lis` AS `nom_lis`,`candidatos`.`can_can` AS `can_can`,`candidatos`.`dis_can` AS `dis_can`,`candidatos`.`ced_asi` AS `ced_asi`,`candidatos`.`nom_asi` AS `nom_asi`,`candidatos`.`tel_asi` AS `tel_asi`,`candidatos`.`mail_asi` AS `mail_asi` from (`candidatos` join `datospersonales`) where (`candidatos`.`ced_per` = `datospersonales`.`ced_per`) ;

-- Estructura para la vista `vistacandidatoscedulas`
--
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `vistacandidatoscedulas`;

CREATE ALGORITHM=UNDEFINED DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` SQL SECURITY DEFINER VIEW `vistacandidatoscedulas`  AS  select `candidatos`.`id_can` AS `id_can`,`datospersonales`.`ced_per` AS `ced_per`,`datospersonales`.`nom_per` AS `nom_per`,`datospersonales`.`mail_per` AS `mail_per`,`datospersonales`.`tel_per` AS `tel_per`,`candidatos`.`dig_can` AS `dig_can`,`candidatos`.`pri_sec` AS `pri_sec`,`candidatos`.`can_can` AS `can_can`,`datospersonales`.`edad_per` AS `edad_per`,`candidatos`.`dis_can` AS `dis_can`,`candidatos`.`ced_asi` AS `ced_asi`,`candidatos`.`nom_asi` AS `nom_asi`,`candidatos`.`tel_asi` AS `tel_asi`,`candidatos`.`mail_asi` AS `mail_asi`,`imagencedula`.`rut_ima` AS `rut_ima`,`imagencedula`.`ima_cit` AS `ima_cit`,`imagencedula`.`id_ima` AS `id_ima` from ((`candidatos` join `datospersonales`) join `imagencedula`) where ((`candidatos`.`ced_per` = `datospersonales`.`ced_per`) and (`imagencedula`.`ced_per` = `datospersonales`.`ced_per`)) ;
